### Root check
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Get all exercises
GET http://localhost:5000/exercises

### Add a new exercise (with schedule)
POST http://localhost:5000/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Back Stretch",
  "description": "Bend forward gently and hold",
  "duration": "4 min",
  "schedule": "2025-08-25T10:00:00Z"
}

### Update an exercise (add/change schedule)
PUT http://localhost:5000/exercises/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Neck Stretch",
  "description": "Gently tilt head side to side",
  "duration": "2 min",
  "schedule": "2025-08-26T08:30:00Z"
}

### Delete an exercise
DELETE http://localhost:5000/exercises/2

### Get all progress
GET http://localhost:5000/progress

### Mark an exercise as done
POST http://localhost:5000/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "exerciseId": 1,
  "date": "2025-08-24"
}
